oxyClass, initialValueBytecode);\n        }\n\n        void addEnterpriseSpecialMethods(ClassFile proxyClass) {\n            addSpecialMethods(proxyClass);\n        }\n    }\n\n    private static class TestBean implements Bean<EnterpriseSessionBean> {\n        @Override\n        public Set<Type> getTypes() {\n            final Set<Type> types = new LinkedHashSet<>();\n            types.add(EnterpriseSessionBean.class);\n            types.add(Object.class);\n            return types;\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public Set<Annotation> getQualifiers() {\n            return Collections.emptySet();\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public Class<? extends Annotation> getScope() {\n            return Dependent.class;\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public String getName() {\n            return null;\n        }\n\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
